climbs.name: Zombie Piglin
climbs.fa: some other bay boy in the 80's

content.description: Variation on Piglin, to the right and up the crack.
content.protection: bring a pad and maybe a buddy
content.location: Park at intersection of paseo del mar and via berri at the cliffs, hike down and follow rocky beach to the left. The climbs are at the little basalt vista.

content.description: sit start into slope-y underclings, beautiful views.
content.protection: bring a pad and maybe a buddy
content.location: Park at intersection of paseo del mar and via berri at the cliffs, hike down and follow rocky beach to the left. The climbs are at the little basalt vista.

climbs.name: Hoglin
climbs.fa: a hermit crab from the tide pools

content.description: Nice little warm-up, can be traversed for more pump.
content.protection: bring a pad and maybe a buddy
content.location: Park at intersection of paseo del mar and via berri at the cliffs, hike down and follow rocky beach to the left. The climbs are at the little basalt vista.

content.description: To the right of Zombie Piglin, this one needs a little more technique. From a sit start the crux is in the first move. The rest is fun.
content.location: Just to the right of Zombie Piglin, about 3 feet, and around the corner.
